    "name": "Jody Wisternoff",
    "profile": "Electronic dance music DJ, composer and producer from Bristol, England. Half of the duo [a=Way Out West] with [a=Nick Warren] and A&R at [l=Anjunadeep].\r\nDuring the early '90s Jody was spinning the decks at raves like Universe and at his three year residency at Lakota Club in Bristol. He produced various styles from dub and hardcore music through trance to deep and progressive house over the years.\r\nSince 2013, he is a mainstay at [l=Anjunadeep], also mixing the [l=Anjunadeep (2)] double CD mix compilation together with [a=James Grant (4)] since [m=579227].",
